                        <interp inst="t18370703-name-521" type="given" value="THOMAS"></interp>THOMAS MARCHANT</persName>
                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">police-constable C</hi> 43.) I took the prisoner—he said he was guilty, and if 4<hi rend="italic">l</hi>. or 5<hi rend="italic">l</hi>. would be of any use to him he would give it him to make it up—he said he was sorry for what he had done, but he was drunk at the time he did it.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner.</hi> I leave it to the mercy of the Court—I have not had time to bring up witnesses—I never was in such a thing in my life.</p>
